    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Black Market. It’s a pumpkin.</i></strong><i> </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Appearing out of nowhere one Winter-cycle, this headgear is the choice of many thugs looking to trick unlucky habbers into giving them treats. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many argue over the Jack-o’-lantern being a fruit or vegetable, when it is in fact a piece of highly flame retardant headgear with interior lit lighting. Ideal for those cool dark nights when you are tempted to get a little too close to the heat of a Magmamaker.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Halloween pack also includes:  </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Skeleton shirt </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Skull Face Tattoo </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This content requires the base game The Ascent on Steam in order to play.</p>",
